# Flarelette JWT Kit

[![npm version](https://img.shields.io/npm/v/@chrislyons-dev/flarelette-jwt.svg?style=flat-square&logo=npm&label=npm)](https://www.npmjs.com/package/@chrislyons-dev/flarelette-jwt)
