## CLI Tools

**Generate HS512 secrets:**

```bash
npx flarelette-jwt-secret --len=64 --dotenv
```

**Generate EdDSA keypairs:**

```bash
npx flarelette-jwt-keygen --kid=ed25519-2025-01
```

